Job description 1 : 
What we’re looking for:

2+ years of hands-on experience designing digital products.
A strong portfolio demonstrating end-to-end product thinking and interaction design—especially in data-heavy or systems-driven environments.
Proficiency in modern design tools (Figma preferred), and ability to prototype and test ideas.
Experience working with or contributing to a design system.
Solid communication and collaboration skills—you can articulate decisions and work effectively with cross-functional teams.
Ability to navigate ambiguity and bring clarity to complex problem spaces.
Comfort with behavioral analytics and a bias toward data-informed design decisions.
Familiarity with AI tools and the ability to thoughtfully integrate them into your workflow.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 2 : 
Design Leadership: Takes ownership of the creative process. Influences designers and non-designers to foster collaboration and alignment, delivering UX artifacts and driving subsystem designs from concept to delivery.
Experience Vision: Craft and present design strategies to stakeholders, balancing user needs, business objectives, and technology feasibility.
Cross-Functional Collaboration: Collaborate with design, research, product managers, and engineers to deliver interaction and visual designs aligned with UX goals.
Design System Advocacy: Promotes and advocates for the adoption of design systems, shares insights, and collaborates with other designers to drive improvements.
Communication & Storytelling: Clearly articulate design work, craft compelling narratives, and foster proactive collaboration. Explore innovative storytelling formats to inspire stakeholders with impactful narratives.
Detail Design & Feedback: Develop task flows, wireframes, prototypes, and other design artifacts to gather feedback and refine designs for maximum user impact. Advocate for iterative improvements to achieve design excellence.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 3 : 
Develop high-quality 3D models of industrial components based on reference drawings, sketches, or concepts.
Generate photorealistic renders optimized for web and print.
Create exploded and rotating animations for marketing and educational purposes.
Work closely with our team to ensure visual output aligns with brand and technical expectations.
Provide output files in multiple formats for different digital platforms.
