Job description 4 : 
Maintaining detailed customer's information for future references for all orders booked.
Recording and reporting any unusual site information or product information in any order to the Supervisor.
Set up master database for all raw material in various software.
Continuously monitor, upgrade the above data
Make site visits in order to make sure the execution is done as per our designs
Readiness to travel all over India whenever required
Calculate BOM for all projects, check material availability in our Inventory and prepare purchase orders for the required material
Maintaining an organised and accessible filing system in computer as well as in physical form.
Staying updated with the latest Product trends and practices.

