Job description 17 : 
Work collaboratively with cross-functional teams to design user-centric product features and enhancements.
Utilize design frameworks and the latest technologies to accelerate product development and launch processes.
Independently work on end-to-end design of product features, from concept ideation to high-fidelity wireframing and prototyping.
Evaluate and recommend innovative design tools and methodologies to optimize design processes and enhance productivity.
Create and maintain a robust design system to ensure consistency, scalability, and efficiency across all product design initiatives.
Develop high-fidelity wireframes, prototypes, and visual designs using industry-standard tools such as Figma.
Conduct usability testing and gather user feedback to iterate on designs and improve the overall user experience.
Present and defend your design decisions. All your design decisions should be based on the overall design roadmap as well as your own design thinking and fundamental principles (i.e. color theory, visual weight, etc.

