Job description 19 : 
Focus on the UX of our Money Management stream and manage expectations with Product and Engineering teams.
Influence Product and Engineering to take up design backlog that eases user pain point or increase delightful experience with micro-interactions.
Work on a diverse problem where analysis and data-driven approach is needed and become a key contributor with Product Manager to stream level strategy and OKRs.
Effectively deliver new feature/improvements for products that are already well-defined in scope.
Define the product briefs and be able to present the ideas/solution to the team.
Document the design process for each feature, such as research findings, ideations, usability testings, release, and monitor the impact after the product release.
Contribute to the team cadence discussion and make a short presentation to the team, as well as present team’s updates if needed.
Proactively seek/give feedback from/to stakeholders to make sure concepts are meeting the intended project goal.

