Job description 23 : 
Employ a user-centric design process in the creation of simple user experiences for complex systems.
You sweat the details and love to work with engineers to create elegant, functional, pixel-perfect results.
You obsess over UX/UI touches that make the customer experience feel human, helpful and delightful.
Estimate time and delivery of projects and tasks.
Create low and high-fidelity UI prototypes that allow users to walk through a user experience at various points throughout the design process.
Assess requirements, alternatives, and risks or benefits for projects. Manage test activities for each application.

